在未来二十年则继续升温，届时将比工业化前的水平高出1.5摄氏度。在这一注定的轨迹下，全世界各地极端天气出现将变得更加频繁和明显。今年夏天，北美的持续高温、西欧和东亚的暴雨洪水、西伯利亚、东地中海的森林大火只是这种未来的预演。 然而，报告中的内容并非都是坏消息——人类仍然可以阻止地球变得更热。若要做到这一点，各国需要协同努力，立即开始迅速放弃化石燃料，到2050年左右停止向大气中排放二氧化碳。报告总结说，假使努力见效，全球变暖的过程很可能会停止，但全球气温仍将比工业化前的水平高出1.5摄氏度左右。联合国气候报告：全球升温已无法避免，极端天气将大幅增加"},"attached_info":"Cj8I5Pii/t6iuZI0EAMaCDY4NjE4NjQxIKqlxIgGMCU4qwNADnIJNDc4NTE4NjM4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"257 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-54f55e6f84ae79699a51761900804231_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"15_1628860471.6399221","card_id":"Q_479242622","target":{"id":479242622,"title":"霍尊在音乐届成就如何，是否达到了自称的「以我今日的身份地位」？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/479242622","type":"question","created":1628753562,"answer_count":925,"follower_count":1591,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[75,105508,132659],"comment_count":120,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"ClUI5Pii/t6iuZI0EAMaCDY4Nzc5NjYwIJqd04gGMHg4twxAD3IJNDc5MjQyNjIyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y","detail_text":"255 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-28e0cf7a18c8be9d249c220e4ea85dba_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"16_1628860471.6403868","card_id":"Q_470628145","target":{"id":470628145,"title":"游戏《永劫无间》的热度会持续多久？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/470628145","type":"question","created":1625632118,"answer_count":75,"follower_count":141,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[553269],"comment_count":1,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"《永劫无间》正式上线需要购买吗，热度还会有以前那么高吗。后续怎么样更新会更好呢？会出PVE吗"},"attached_info":"Cj8I5Pi